+/* IPV4_UPDATE with the TTL bit always set (this manip's
+ * purpose is OH-port L3 forwarding; TTL-- is mandatory).
+ * Cross-ref SDK fm_manip.c case
+ * e_FM_PCD_MANIP_HDR_FIELD_UPDATE_IPV4 (TTL path).
