+/* ---- TEST: MANIP_FIELD_UPDATE_IPV4_FORWARD (v1.2) ------------- */
+/*
+ * Canonical OH-port stage-3 primitive: TTL-- with auto-cksum
+ * recompute, no DSCP rewrite.  Encoded as a single IPV4_UPDATE
+ * command word with TTL+CS_CALC bits set, no inline payload.
+ *
+ * Silicon-fact pin: the encoded word MUST equal 0x0c040001 because
+ *   (OP_IPV4_UPDATE=0x0c) << 24
+ *   | IP_L4_CS_CALC=0x00040000
+ *   | IPV4_UPDATE_TTL=0x00000001
