+/* ---- TEST: MANIP_FIELD_UPDATE_IPV4_FORWARD + DSCP (v1.2) ------ */
+/*
+ * Same primitive but with the DSCP-rewrite arm exercised.  Verifies:
+ *   - the DSCP operand bit (0x04) is OR'd into the command word
+ *   - the inline payload word carries the DSCP value left-shifted
+ *     to bit position 26 (HMCD_IPV4_DSCP_SHIFT)
+ *   - the auto-cksum bit is ALSO set (TTL is touched -> cksum must
+ *     be recomputed; DSCP-only rewrites with no TTL are not a
+ *     supported configuration on this manip)
+ *   - DSCP > 63 is rejected at the encoder (silicon only has 6 bits)
